Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:09.61,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}囁く天使は堕ちて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:16.71,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}優しく食むわ　あなたの全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:35.26,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}気づく　目を見開いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.74,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}仄青い混凝土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:40.22,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}冷たく私を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:45.20,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}そして抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:51.74,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}あなたのいないその体で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:54.54,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}吐き出しその生命は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:22:01.89,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}まだ形を残しているわ　紅く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:04.51,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}鮮やかな永遠が見えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:08.59,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}隣でそれは歌いだすわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.71,0:22:15.51,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}ねえ　私を愛して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:20.11,ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}離さないから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:02.45,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}All is calm All is bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:09.61,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}在耳边细语的天使堕入凡间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:16.71,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}我会将你温柔地蚕食殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:21.91,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}It's my guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:35.26,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}回过神 眼瞳空洞地睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.74,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}这暗蓝色的混凝土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:40.22,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}冰冷地将我包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:42.68,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}Call my name and give me a kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:45.20,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}而后将我揽入胸怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:51.74,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}用你那已经失去灵魂的躯体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:54.54,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}濒临崩溃的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:22:01.89,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}仍勉强维持姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:04.51,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}我能看见那赤红绚丽的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:08.59,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}它就在我身旁放声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:11.71,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}What was I born for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.71,0:22:15.51,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}请深爱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:20.11,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}我绝不离开你
